erage in workflow-engine.ts not separately measured (tested via 17 integration tests)\n132\t- Pre-existing: stats.test.ts failure, lint require-yield error in workflow-engine.test.ts\n133\t\n134\tToken Report: 14 tool calls (Bash: 9, Read: 1, Grep: 3, Write: 1). 1 unique file. Coverage run twice (first without filter).\n135\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_019Ci4zjEoXjT3zPnFFZP7Tk","session_id":"3330d992-072a-4898-af8b-5f3f7e12cbac","uuid":"c698892c-adf1-4805-be49-fe73903311bd","timestamp":"2026-04-03T18:00:29.178Z"}
